  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Office Cleaner",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Perform daily office cleaning duties to ensure a clean and tidy working environment, including vacuuming/ sweeping, mopping the floors, dusting, wiping tables, clearing trash bins, cleaning office glass doors, windows (reachable areas) and partitions.</p></li><li><p>Clean designated areas including the Managing Director’s, Directors’ and Manager’s rooms, pantry, meeting rooms, office common areas.</p></li><li><p>Carry out periodically cleaning of pantry appliances such as refrigerator, microwave, oven, coffee machine etc.</p></li><li><p>Empty all trash and recycling bins and ensure proper disposal of waste.</p></li><li><p>Refill pantry supplies (e.g. biscuits, coffee, tea, kitchen towels) when required.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Report any maintenance issues, damages or low supplies to the Supervisor.</p></li><li><p>Perform other ad hoc duties as assigned by Management or Supervisor.<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong> Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>No formal education required.</p></li><li><p>Relevant cleaning or housekeeping experience is an advantage.</p></li><li><p>Ability to handle basic cleaning equipment and materials.</p></li><li><p>Able to perform cleaning tasks including standing, bending, lifting and carrying cleaning equipment.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Able to work independently with minimal supervision.</p></li><li><p>Responsible, reliable and punctual.</p></li><li><p>No work pass quota<br /></p></li></ul><p> <strong>Working Hours:</strong></p><p>Monday to Friday: 8am to 5pm (incl. 1hr lunch break)</p>",
